name: thedailybeast
text:
Portnoy, who made sure to point out that his nickname is “El Presidente,” asked if the actual president ever tweets something out and then wakes up the next day and thinks, “Aw man, I wish I didn’t send that one out.” 

“Often,” Trump replied. “Too often.” https://t.co/WmuXX4tcNQ

name: thedailybeast
text: Shortly before the summer kicked off, Donald Trump was hopeful about an economic revival. But it all came crashing down, with the president canceling the RNC and admitting to the American people that he was throwing in the towel. https://t.co/qpZr30NSCt
